# For more info on HTTP files go to https://aka.ms/vs/httpfile
### Test Hello World (HTTP -> should redirect to HTTPS)
GET http://localhost:5924/

### Test Hello World (HTTPS)
GET https://localhost:5925/

### Test Circuit Breaker (giả lập nhiều request đồng thời)
GET https://localhost:5925/api/test?load=heavy

### Test Input Validation (query chứa XSS - đã URL-encode)
GET http://localhost:5924/api/test?query=%3Cscript%3Ealert(%27xss%27)%3C%2Fscript%3E

### Test Input Validation (query chứa SQL injection - đã URL-encode space)
GET http://localhost:5924/api/test?query=DROP%20TABLE%20Users

### Test Secure Query (không có flag secure -> allowed)
GET http://localhost:5924/api/test

### Test Secure Query (có flag secure=false -> should be blocked with 400)
GET http://localhost:5924/api/test?secure=false

### Test Secure Query (có flag secure=true -> allowed; try HTTPS)
GET https://localhost:5925/api/test?secure=true

### Test Delay Request (giả lập trễ 2000ms)
GET https://localhost:5925/api/test?delay=2000

# Notes:
# - If you test the HTTP endpoints (port 5924) you should see redirects to https://localhost:5925 for endpoints that trigger UseHttpsRedirection.
# - Some clients (including the VS HTTP file runner) may not follow redirects automatically — inspect the response status and the `Location` header.
# - All queries with spaces or special characters are URL-encoded to avoid HTTP parsing errors.
